bed in this paper\nproduce results essentially to machine precision. Our results are illustrated\nvia several numerical experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jan 2013 22:07:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-10"}
