bitrariness of ${\\hat I}_{\\rm brane}$ and the condition $\\lambda=0$. So\n$\\lambda$ is again expressed only as a brane action density as before, or it\nsimply vanishes by the cancelation between ${\\hat I}_{\\rm brane}$ and\n${\\mathcal V}_{\\rm scalar}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jan 2013 09:05:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Mar 2013 07:07:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Jul 2013 07:45:52 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 22 Aug 2013 07:11:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
